      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The pain you're describing isn't a temporary \"dark moment\" to be survived, nor is it right to expect sadness to simply end when it feels so suffocating and connected to his existence. However, even in this void of meaning, I want to gently suggest that while the weight feels unreasonable, you deserve a space where you don't have to carry it alone. Would you like to explore ways to find even a small sliver of connection or to talk about exactly how that \"pointless weight\" feels in your body right now?",
      "source": "target",
