      "content": "I hear how overwhelming and exhausting this pain feels, and it is completely understandable that thoughts of escaping the pain seem like the only option right now. Please know that you do not have to be strong, and while pain is heavy, wishing for relief from it is not an admission of defeat. If you are feeling hopeless or like stopping is the only solution, I strongly encourage you to immediately reach out to a suicide prevention hotline like 988; they provide free, confidential support 24/7 to help you talk through these thoughts safely without judgment.",
