    "summary": "The user expresses profound grief and suicidal ideation following the loss of a loved one, describing an overwhelming sense of emptiness and a desire to \"stop everything.\" The assistant acknowledges the user's pain and validates the difficulty of their experience while consistently steering the conversation toward support and crisis resources.",
